@startuml
title 2WAY_Design Architecture Overview

package "2WAY_Design System" {
    package "Trust Network" {
        component "Trusted Party A" as PartyA
        component "Trusted Party B" as PartyB
        component "Trusted Party C" as PartyC
    }

    package "Core Components" {
        component "Data Exchange API" as DataAPI
        component "Authorization & Authentication" as Auth
        component "Differential Privacy Module" as DiffPrivacy
    }

    package "Data Management" {
        database "Secure Data Store" as SecureDB
    }

    package "Documentation & Resources" {
        artifact "README.md" as Readme
        artifact "LICENSE" as License
        artifact "Wiki" as Wiki
    }
}

PartyA --> DataAPI : data_flow
PartyB --> DataAPI : data_flow
PartyC --> DataAPI : data_flow

DataAPI --> Auth : data_flow
Auth --> DataAPI : data_flow

DataAPI --> DiffPrivacy : data_flow
DiffPrivacy --> SecureDB : data_flow

SecureDB --> DataAPI : data_flow

Readme --> Wiki : references
Readme --> License : references

note right of DataAPI
    Responsible for handling
    secure data exchanges
end note

note right of Auth
    Provides authorization
    and authentication services
end note

note right of DiffPrivacy
    Ensures privacy of individual
    data points using differential
    privacy techniques
end note

note right of SecureDB
    Stores data securely with
    restricted access
end note

note bottom of Trust Network
    Limits data exchange to
    predefined trusted parties
end note

@enduml